			  	When you station ships on a planet they won't defend unless there are some ships on standby first. So what happens is they take the planet and your ships go on standby. If you had some fleets on standby, those that were on standby and those that were stationed would simultanioulsy defend, allowing the possibility of more then 20 fleets defending. 			   <P align=right></P>
